# ğŸ”Œ 4. Backend API Endpoints (Useful for Testing)

### **Backend Root**

```
http://127.0.0.1:8000/
```

### **API Docs (USE THIS TO TEST BACKEND MANUALLY)**

```
http://127.0.0.1:8000/docs
```

### **Endpoints Available**

| Feature          | Method | URL                |
| ---------------- | ------ | ------------------ |
| Register User    | POST   | `/users/register`  |
| Add Habit        | POST   | `/habits/add`      |
| List User Habits | GET    | `/habits/list`     |
| Complete Habit   | POST   | `/habits/complete` |
| Leaderboard      | GET    | `/leaderboard/`    |

---

# ğŸ—‘ï¸ 5. Resetting / Recreating the Database (IMPORTANT)

You must reset the database when:

* You modify `models.py`
* Add new tables
* Add new fields
* Change column types

### **Commands (run from `/backend` folder)**

#### **Delete Existing SQLite DB File**

```sh
del habit_arena.db            # Windows
```

or

```sh
Remove-Item habit_arena.db -Force
```

#### **Start Backend Again**

```sh
uvicorn app.main:app --reload
```

A new database will be created automatically.

---

# ğŸ“‚ 6. Important File Structure Overview

### **Backend: (`backend/app/`)**

* `main.py` â†’ FastAPI application, router setup
* `models.py` â†’ User & Habit database models
* `database.py` â†’ SQLite engine & initialization
* `routers/users.py` â†’ Register user
* `routers/habits.py` â†’ Add habit, list habits, complete habits
* `routers/leaderboard.py` â†’ Leaderboard rankings
* `utils/points.py` â†’ Points & rewards logic

### **Frontend: (`frontend/`)**

* `login.html` â†’ User login (auto-registers)
* `dashboard.html` â†’ Habit list, add habits, complete habits
* `style.css` â†’ UI styling
* `script.js` â†’ All API calls & UI logic

