# ğŸ‰ 8. Summary of All Key Commands

### Start Backend

```sh
cd backend
habit_arena_venv\Scripts\activate
uvicorn app.main:app --reload
```

### Start Frontend

```sh
cd frontend
python -m http.server 3000
```

### Reset Database

```sh
cd backend
del habit_arena.db
uvicorn app.main:app --reload
```

### Open UI

```
http://127.0.0.1:3000/login.html
http://127.0.0.1:3000/dashboard.html
```

